                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18680921-866-offence-1 t18680921-name-527"></join>John Marks</persName>, and stealing a watch, chain, and key, his property, Collins having been before convicted; to which </rs>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">COLLINS</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18680921-866-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18680921-866-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18680921-866-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="pleadedGuilty"></interp>PLEADED GUILTY</rs>
